# kind

**Instance Property**

The kind representation of this generated content.

## Declaration

```swift
var kind: GeneratedContent.Kind { get }
```

## Discussion

This property provides access to the content in a strongly-typed enum representation, preserving the hierarchical structure of the data and the  data’s [doc://com.apple.foundationmodels/documentation/FoundationModels/GenerationID] ids.

## Accessing instance properties

- **isComplete**: A Boolean that indicates whether the generated content is completed.
- **jsonString**: Returns a JSON string representation of the generated content.
